[[Translation:en/Manual/Base Set/Railways]]
'''Railways''' are the primary transport tool at your disposal. Versatile and efficient, railways allow [[en/Manual/Trains]] to move around with unlimited amounts of [[en/Manual/Cargo]].

There are four types of rail track.

'''Standard Railways''' will support steam and diesel trains.

'''Electrified Railways''' will support steam, diesel and electric trains.

'''Monorail''' will support Monorail trains only. There are only two Monorail available.

'''Maglev''' will support Maglev trains only. There are five maglev trains available.